### ====================== BLOG ROUTES ======================

### Get all blogs
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs

### Get featured blogs
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs/featured

### Get blogs by tag
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs/tag/tagId

### Get blogs by user
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs/user/userId

### Get a single blog by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs/blogId

### Create a new blog
POST {{baseUrl}}/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

